{"tid":1737283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府成日賣廣告就當做左野, 點解黎一招順水推舟?","createTime":"2019-11-19T02:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:35:35.000Z","uid":123926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"670b5456d65f0e9416769a0d2a678fd42cc4218d","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"學美國嘅議員話齋, <br />\n以前我地有好多有創意嘅抗爭方便,<br />\n點解而家全部都淨係打陣地戰呢?<br />\n自六月以黎政府落左有幾多款廣告已經多到唔記得, <br />\n最新一款 「與暴力割蓆」何不反過黎用黎做文宣? <br />\n宣傳返狂暴警察同政府嘅制度暴力<br />\n上次塞完機場嘅道歉大會贏得全球掌聲,<br />\n今次可以再下一城,<br />\n先為民生影響道歉 &gt; 解釋原因係由於政府同狂暴警察首先發狂, 我地無奈下唯有還擊 &gt; 提出六月以黎收集到嘅証據 &gt;「與制度暴力割蓆」<br />\n咁做可以令到前線有機會休息,<br />\n又可以俾國際知道我地唔係暴徒,<br />\n我地都唔想影響到民生,<br />\n由頭到尾都係俾政府逼成, 係政府一手做成嘅"},{"pid":"77ec9faaadb0cd7e8c8bd9df01def178cd1883cb","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"自推 10次<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"f3847ea17703028605f4f1044367c13e6f2ba1ed","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"672b95e31aa17420918c6d8e6fd3baa0237f8422","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cf22de57f1d2c175119e7cab0154ace0177024b2","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"ce53acdc7a44ae525a046155baf740e35f885b5c","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"a3ed11577f75e38c7ed2f046314059fedf826893","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c05446a5e6cc3479dedb7360e2d6606e4d7d91f6","tid":1737283,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"5693d4f284ac90fbb6e9a4af